    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> free range chicken breast portion[s]</strong> to a chopping board and cover with a sheet of <strong>cling film</strong></p><p>Bash the<strong> chicken</strong> with a <strong>rolling pin</strong> until evenly flattened – this is your<strong> chicken escalope</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
