            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> panko breadcrumbs</strong> and <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong> to a plate and season with <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Spread your<strong> Dijon mustard </strong>over both sides of the chicken escalope using the back of a spoon</p><p>Press the <strong>chicken escalope</strong> into the <strong>breadcrumbs</strong> firmly to evenly coat all over – this is your <strong>breaded chicken</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
