      "instruction": "<p>Fill the <strong>warmed brioche bun</strong> with the <strong>free range</strong> <strong>chicken schnitzel </strong>and some<strong> apple & dill slaw</strong></p><p>Serve with the <strong>chips </strong>and any <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>apple & dill slaw </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
